		' Deleting ArgoCD ApplicationSets:, ' \
		' Created by Makefile_Setup_ArgoCD_ApplicationSets_Using_Git_Generator:' \
		' myapp-single-cluster-envs (if they exist)...';
	@kubectl delete applicationset myapp-single-cluster-envs -n $(ARGOCD_NAMESPACE) --ignore-not-found